thaaiku oru thaalaattu ( english : lullaby to the mother ) is a 1986 indian tamil film , directed by balachandra menon and produced by k. r. gangadharan . the film stars sivaji ganesan , padmini , visu and pandiyan in lead roles . the film had musical score by ilayaraja . the film was a remake of director 's own malayalam film oru painkilikatha .